But surely you've read _Watership Down_...in which the rabbits bound along in a looose-limbed fashion....  a relaxed LOLLOPing pace....

@Peter

I often get an inexplicably good time when solving the crossword puzzle.

Oh, you mean, the completion time!  On June 20, 2023, which happens to be my birthday, the time posted for my solve is 0:00.  You can't do much better than that, unless you solve it before you open it.

@Peter
I have seen the opposite, where I'll complete a puzzle in like 30 minutes, come here to talk about it, and when I go back to the puzzle my time is 50 minutes.

This would be pretty annoying if I actually cared about my time. My heart goes out to the speed-solvers.

