The "party" in D&D is the group of characters you're all playing as, like Mike the Paladin, Jess the Wizard, etc. Visiting a TAVERN  is something you can do in-game, to get supplies and information.

Going to a bar to "pick up new leads" is actually a pretty common trope in entertainment. Think of a detective questioning a bartender who is eternally drying a beer glass.

@Mean Old Lady 

